PornServ posts porn from Reddit (and maybe other sites one day!) to IRC. 
No need to explain why this is great.

Usage:
$ pornserv
    --server irc.rizon.net
    --port 6697
    --nick nick
    --username username
    --realname realname
    --password nickservpassword (Optional)
    --channel "#channel,#channel2"
    --interval 60 (Post time in minutes)
    --reddit Subreddit,Subreddit2 (Case sensitive)
	
Requires:
    python 3
    aiocron
    irc3
    praw 3.4.0
